ActCustoms Act
SubjectCEFTA Verification of Origin of Exported Goods Regulations
PrecisCEFTA VERIFICATION OF ORIGIN OF EXPORTED GOODS REGULATIONS in order to incorporate the CANADA-EUROPEAN FREE TRADE ASSOCIATION FREE TRADE AGREEMENT (CEFTA) into Canada's existing regulatory framework by allowing customs procedures related to rules of origin to be administered in accordance with the terms of the CEFTA.
